      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and truly looks like it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a showroom-quality shine, and the interior is immaculate, featuring pristine upholstery and a cabin that still smells new. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment with a full service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in such impeccable, investment-grade condition.",
