    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a parts donor. The engine currently has a severe head gasket leak and a significant misfire that makes it unreliable for daily use. Externally, the body shows heavy rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling across most surfaces. The interior requires a complete overhaul, as the upholstery is torn and there is a persistent musty odor. It will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
